<view class="pay_page">
  <view class="payCard">
    <view class="head">
      <image src="{{logo}}"></image>
      <view class="infobox">
        <view class="storeTitle"> {{storeTitle}}</view>
        <view class="price"> ￥{{price}}元</view>
      </view>
    </view>
    <view class="codeWrap">
      <view class="tip">扫描下面的二维码收款</view>
      <canvas style="width: 200px; height: 200px;" canvas-id="myQrcode"></canvas>
    </view>
  </view>
  <view class="intros">
    <view class="title">说明：</view>
    <view>1. 从账户余额自动扣款。</view>
    <view>2. 付款前请先核对信息是否一致。</view>
    <view>3. 更多详细说明，请联系客服。</view>
  </view>
</view>